己.definition: self; oneself; sixth of the ten Heavenly Stems 十天干[shi2 tian1 gan1]; sixth in order; letter "F" or Roman "VI" in list "A, B, C", or "I, II, III" etc; hexa

己丑.definition: twenty-sixth year F2 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 2009 or 2069

己亥.definition: thirty-sixth year F12 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1959 or 2019

己卯.definition: sixteenth year F4 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1999 or 2059

己巳.definition: sixth year F6 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1989 or 2049

己所不欲，勿施於人.pinyin: ji3 suo3 bu4 yu4 , wu4 shi1 yu2 ren2
己所不欲，勿施於人.definition: What you don't want done to you, don't do to others. (idiom, from the Confucian analects); Do as you would be done by.; Do not do to others what you would not have them do to you.

己未.definition: fifty-sixth year F8 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1979 or 2039

己糖.definition: hexose (CH2O)6, monosaccharide with six carbon atoms, such as glucose 葡萄糖[pu2 tao5 tang2]

己酉.definition: forty-sixth year F10 of the 60 year cycle, e.g. 1969 or 2029
